    "title": "Senior Plant Manager at Nestle India",
    "description": "Nestle India has an exciting opening for a Plant Manager at our Vijayawada office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Nestle India:\nNestle India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Coordinate with design and engineering teams on product improvements\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• BPharm / MPharm / PharmD\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in FMEA\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Referral bonus program\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Vijayawada, Andhra Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Nestle India!",
